  "texts": [
    "• Indeterminate lymph nodes are assumed to be possible malignancy (ambiguous).",
    "• Those notes that were written in a foreign language were excluded from the adjudication.",
    "• 'Glioma' is typically indicative of possible malignancy (ambiguous), as it might be benign or malignant.",
    "However, if it has been described with a qualifier that signals benign (e.g.",
    "low-grade glioma or benign glioma), it has been deemed as 'no malignancy'."
  ]
